&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 4 Pharmacy Technician/Aseptic Operator&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Looking for a change or some extra experience?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a technician/operator to work in our aseptic unit at Hammersmith Hospital and Charing Cross Hospital&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your main role will be to assist in the provision of cytotoxic chemotherapy, parenteral nutrition and clinical trials within our licensed aseptic units.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In conjunction with our other team members you will ensure that the aseptic service is provided to chemotherapy and nutrition patients across the trust to a high standard. This will include compounding of chemotherapy, clinical trials and parenteral nutrition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Specific roles will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Processing cytotoxic, PN and trial worksheets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Undertake the compounding of aseptically prepared products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Supervision and Training of Pharmacy Assistants and Pre-registration Pharmacy Technicians.&lt;/p&gt;
